{"tid":2429303,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"DeepFuckingValue 被註銷金融經紀執照","createTime":"2021-03-02T07:58:52.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-02T08:05:21.000Z","uid":28765,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"c26321d6a3b4bbee056f2c3e520a70c7fc4916f3","tid":2429303,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T07:58:52.000Z","msg":"據《路透社》報導，因GameStop軋空戰一戰成名的吉爾（Keith Gill），據了解已不再是美國金融業監管局（Financial Industry Regulatory Authority, FINRA）下註冊的金融經紀人。<br />\n<br />\n根據FINRA數據顯示，截至2月26日，吉爾已不再是經註冊的金融經紀人。據報導，在失去金融經紀人身分後，吉爾不再能夠代表客戶買賣證券，並且也不能夠作為投資人顧問，向客戶提供證券相關建議。對此消息吉爾並未立即回覆評論請求。<br />\n<br />\n......<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/property/20210302/3CZAUXRJF5CO5AGBDUDIZTVIIE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fproperty%2F20210302%2F3CZAUXRJF5CO5AGBDUDIZTVIIE%2F&d=a689Ea%2B9Xr9H89nGruQQAxURuvs7l%2FVEN9tydxl6KII%3D&h=c84020f1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fproperty%2F20210302%2F3CZAUXRJF5CO5AGBDUDIZTVIIE%2F&h=7129213f\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/property/20210302/3CZAUXRJF5CO5AGBDUDIZTVIIE/</a>"},{"pid":"81ceda7b691de1ca5b7704e53d9d8b00b3c9b5af","tid":2429303,"uid":9901,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T07:59:40.000Z","msg":"佢上次hearing有講左佢唔係broker<br />\n點樣被註銷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9b89fc84a963e6bd161c77ee137f91b10bd146f","tid":2429303,"uid":255543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T07:59:57.000Z","msg":"賺夠退休<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bed0708b89145170658e5fd6e65634073214b2eb","tid":2429303,"uid":123774,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T08:00:11.000Z","msg":"佢唔係1月離左職咩"},{"pid":"74272